    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "稅後營運溢利增長5%至59.42億美元，產生的基本自由盈餘則上升7%至58.43億美元，反映我們擁有高質素的\n經常性盈利來源。內涵價值權益創新高，達672億美元。截至2020年12月31日，集團當地資本總和法覆蓋率為\n374%，足證我們雄厚的資本實力和嚴謹的財務管理。",
    "current_translation": "OPAT increased by 5% to US$5.942 billion, with underlying free surplus generation (UFSG) rising by 7% to US$5.843 billion, reflecting our high-quality recurring earnings sources. EV Equity reached a record high of US$67.2 billion. As at 31 December 2020, the Group LCSM cover ratio stood at 374%, demonstrating our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
  },
